Package com.gmail.etordera.jcms

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IccProfile
    Representation of an ICC color profile.

    This class uses native LittleCMS C library for managing ICC profile data, and may allocate resources that will not be automatically freed by JVM's garbage collection.
    IccTransform
    Represents an ICC color transformation operation.

    This class uses native LittleCMS C library for managing ICC color transformations, and may allocate resources that will not be automatically freed by JVM's garbage collection.
    IccTransformer
    An IccTransformer performs ICC color transformation on images.

    This class uses native LittleCMS C library for managing ICC color transformations, and may allocate resources that will not be automatically freed by JVM's garbage collection.
    JCMS
    Utility class for the JavaCMS library.

    Defines common constants and provides JNI access to LittleCMS library.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    JCMSException
    Custom Exception class for errors detected in JCMS classes.
